dreisoft.tresos.tresosdb.api.model

Class DBModelUpgrade

  • java.lang.Object
    • dreisoft.tresos.lib2.api.util.AbstractExecutableExtension
      • dreisoft.tresos.tresosdb.api.model.DBModelUpgrade
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    org.eclipse.core.runtime.IExecutableExtension

    public class DBModelUpgrade
extends AbstractExecutableExtension
    This class can be registered to the tresosdb upgrade extension-point to provide database upgrades.

public void init(TresosDB tresosDB,

                              java.lang.String modelTypeNew)
        Deprecated. internal API
        Called by the registry to initialize the class. Used for upgrading to a new meta-model version of the tresosDB
        Parameters:
        tresosDB - the tresosDB providing the source data
        tresosDBNew - tresosDB in which the upgraded data will reside. If null, the upgrade will operate directly on (source) tresosDB
        metaModelVersionOld - the version from which to upgrade
        metaModelVersionNew - the version to which to upgrade
        modelTypeNew - model type to which is upgraded
        Since:
        2009.a

                                            APIOperationStatus upgradeStatus)
        Deprecated. internal API
        Called by the registry to initialize the class. Used for upgrading to a new tresosDB type (i.e. the model attributes in the version info change).
        Parameters:
        tresosDB - the tresosDB providing the source data
        tresosDBNewFile - tresosDB File in which the upgraded data will reside.
        metaModelVersionOld - the version from which to upgrade
        metaModelVersionNew - the version to which to upgrade
        modelTypeNew - model type to which is upgraded
        upgradeStatus - can be used by upgrader to add status messages
